<L>The distant thunder's roaring, the blue lightnings vivid fl<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"></L>
<L>And <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ockey mountains fall from high, hark! hark! <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> dreadful crash;</L>
<L>The earth does tremble beneath us, oh! pardon us our si<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"></L>
