<L><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> earthquake's uncap'd the mountain's top, see fire <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">rsting forth!</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> burning lumps of sulphur are bel<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">h'd from out the earth,</L>
